    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate (don't chop!) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and grate (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>cornflour </strong>and 2 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[110ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[110ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>milk </strong>and whisk well – this is your <strong>cornflour mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
