            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the peas are hot</p><p>Once hot, mash the peas with a squeeze of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lime </strong>juice until they come together nicely – these are your <strong>coconut</strong> <strong>mushy peas</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1642760668727-x200.jpg",
