            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>grated ginger</strong>, <strong>grated garlic</strong> and <strong>curry powder</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cornflour mix </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until reduced and glossy – this is your <strong>chip shop curry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
