    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Indian-style fish </strong>with the<strong> chips</strong>,<strong> coconut</strong> <strong>mushy peas </strong>and a little bowl of<strong> chip shop curry sauce </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
